  /*************************************************************************/
  /*                                                                       */
  /* <Type>                                                                */
  /*    FT_Face_Internal                                                   */
  /*                                                                       */
  /* <Description>                                                         */
  /*    An opaque handle to an `FT_Face_InternalRec' structure that models */
  /*    the private data of a given @FT_Face object.                       */
  /*                                                                       */
  /*    This structure might change between releases of FreeType~2 and is  */
